---
// Modern Footer Component - Inspired by Antfu's clean design approach
---

<footer class="bg-secondary border-t border-primary">
  <div class="container py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand Column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-bold text-primary">Pixelated Empathy</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-secondary">AI-Powered Mental Health</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary mb-6">
          Revolutionizing mental health education through advanced AI simulation and immersive training experiences.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://github.com" class="text-secondary hover:text-primary transition-colors">
